      "role": "user",
      "content": "poetic is a weird way to put it... but i guess i get what u mean. it's just that the more i think about it, the less heavy it feels. like, if i just stopped being here, the silence would be so much more peaceful than this constant feeling of being out of place. everyone's just moving on without me anyway.",
